title: Cosmic Connections (Time-Life Mysteries of the Unknown)
description:
pdf / English / 1988 Time-Life / 160 pages / ISBN 10 0809463407 / 33.3 mb

As usual with Time-Life books, this is an excellent objective review of the history and components of a subject that is controversial. Whether you believe in astrology or not, this book details the influential thinkers on the study of the planets and universe in a fascinating manner that does not come across as favorable or skeptical
